trans-unit.target: Napaka pri nalaganju podatkov o sredstvih.

trans-unit.source: Building a mempool and blockchain explorer for the Bitcoin community, focusing on the transaction fee market and multi-layer ecosystem, without any advertising, altcoins, or third-party trackers.
trans-unit.target: Raziskovalec blokov in mempool-a razvit za Bitcoin skupnost, osredotočen na trg omrežnin za transakcije in večplastni ekosistem. Brez oglaševanja, alternativnih kriptovalut in sledilcev tretjih ponudnikov.

trans-unit.source: The number of transactions on this address exceeds the Electrum server limit Consider viewing this address on the official Mempool website instead:
trans-unit.target: Število transakcij povezanih s tem naslovom presega omejitev Electrum strežnika Oglejte si ta naslov na uradni spletni strani Mempoola:

trans-unit.source: Returns details about an address. Available fields: address, chain_stats, and mempool_stats. chain,mempool_stats each contain an object with tx_count, funded_txo_count, funded_txo_sum, spent_txo_count, and spent_txo_sum.
trans-unit.target: Vrne podatke o naslovu. Razpoložljiva polja: address, chain_stats, in mempool_stats. chain,mempool_stats vsebujeta objekt z tx_count, funded_txo_count, funded_txo_sum, spent_txo_count, in spent_txo_sum.

trans-unit.source: Get transaction history for the specified address/scripthash, sorted with newest first. Returns up to 50 mempool transactions plus the first 25 confirmed transactions. You can request more confirmed transactions using :last_seen_txid (see below).
trans-unit.target: Pridobi zgodovino transakcij za podan naslov/scripthash, urejeno po času, najnovejša na začetku. Vrne do 50 mempool ter prvih 25 potrjenih transakcij. Z uporabo :last_seen_txid je mogoče pridobiti več potrjenih transakcij (glej spodaj).

trans-unit.source: Get confirmed transaction history for the specified address/scripthash, sorted with newest first. Returns 25 transactions per page. More can be requested by specifying the last txid seen by the previous query.
trans-unit.target: Pridobi zgodovino potrjenih transakcij za podan naslov/scripthash, urejeno po času, najnovejša na začetku. Vrne 25 transakcij na stran. Več jih je mogoče pridobiti z navedbo zadnjega vrnjenega txid-ja.

trans-unit.source: Get unconfirmed transaction history for the specified address/scripthash. Returns up to 50 transactions (no paging).
trans-unit.target: Pridobi zgodovino nepotrjenih transakcij za podan naslov/scripthash. Vrne do 50 transakcij (brez ostranjevanja, angl. paging).

trans-unit.source: Get the list of unspent transaction outputs associated with the address/scripthash. Available fields: txid, vout, value, and status (with the status of the funding tx).There is also a valuecommitment field that may appear in place of value, plus the following additional fields: asset/assetcommitment, nonce/noncecommitment, surjection_proof, and range_proof.
trans-unit.target: Vrne seznam neporabljenih izhodov transakcij povezanih z naslovom/scripthash. Razpoložljiva polja: txid, vout, value, in status (stanje potrditve transakcije). Polje valuecommitment lahko nadomešča value. Dodatna polja: asset/assetcommitment, nonce/noncecommitment, surjection_proof, in range_proof.

trans-unit.source: Returns information about a Liquid asset.

Returns transactions associated with the specified Liquid asset. For the network's native asset, returns a list of peg in, peg out, and burn transactions. For user-issued assets, returns a list of issuance, reissuance, and burn transactions. Does not include regular transactions transferring this asset.
trans-unit.target: Vrne transakcije povezane s podanim Liquid sredstvom. Za izvorno sredstvo omrežja, vrne seznam peg in, peg out, in burn transakcij. Za uporabniško izdana sredstva, vrne seznam izdajnih, transakcij ponovne izdaje in burn transakcij. Ne vključuje rednih transakcij prenosa tega sredstva.

trans-unit.source: Get the current total supply of the specified asset. For the native asset (L-BTC), this is calculated as [chain,mempool]_stats.peg_in_amount - [chain,mempool]_stats.peg_out_amount - [chain,mempool]_stats.burned_amount. For issued assets, this is calculated as [chain,mempool]_stats.issued_amount - [chain,mempool]_stats.burned_amount. Not available for assets with blinded issuances. If /decimal is specified, returns the supply as a decimal according to the asset's divisibility. Otherwise, returned in base units.
trans-unit.target: Pridobi trenutni znesek v obtoku za podano sredstvo. Za izvorno sredstvo (L-BTC), je izračunan kot [chain,mempool]_stats.peg_in_amount - [chain,mempool]_stats.peg_out_amount - [chain,mempool]_stats.burned_amount. Za izdana sredstva pa [chain,mempool]_stats.issued_amount - [chain,mempool]_stats.burned_amount. Ni na voljo za sredstva z zaupnim zneskom izdaje. Če je podan /decimal, vrne znesek na število decimalnih mest sredstva natančno. Sicer vrnjeno v osnovnih enotah.

trans-unit.source: Returns details about a block. Available fields: id, height, version, timestamp, bits, nonce, merkle_root, tx_count, size, weight,proof, and previousblockhash.
trans-unit.target: Vrne podatke o bloku. Razpoložljiva polja: id, height, version, timestamp, bits, nonce, merkle_root, tx_count, size, weight,proof, in previousblockhash.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash of the block currently at :height.
trans-unit.target: Vrne zgoščeno vrednost (hash) bloka na višini :height.

trans-unit.source: Returns the raw block representation in binary.
trans-unit.target: Vrne neobdelane podatke o bloku v binarni obliki.

trans-unit.source: Returns the confirmation status of a block. Available fields: in_best_chain (boolean, false for orphaned blocks), next_best (the hash of the next block, only available for blocks in the best chain).
trans-unit.target: Vrne stanje potrditve bloka. Razpoložljiva polja: in_best_chain (boolean, false za osirotele bloke, angl. orphaned), next_best (zgoščena vrednost oz. hash naslednjega bloka, na voljo samo za bloke v veljavni verigi).

trans-unit.source: Returns the height of the last block.
Returns the hash of the last block.
Returns the transaction at index :index within the specified block.
trans-unit.target: Vrne transakcijo z zaporedno številko :index znotraj podanega bloka.

trans-unit.source: Returns a list of all txids in the block.
trans-unit.target: Vrne seznam vseh txid-jev v bloku.

trans-unit.source: Returns a list of transactions in the block (up to 25 transactions beginning at start_index). Transactions returned here do not have the status field, since all the transactions share the same block and confirmation status.
trans-unit.target: Vrne seznam transakcij v bloku (do 25 transakcij z začetkom start_index). Podatki o transakciji ne vsebujejo polja status, saj gre za transakcije istega bloka z istim številom potrditev.

trans-unit.source: Returns the 10 newest blocks starting at the tip or at :start_height if specified.
trans-unit.target: Vrne 10 najnovejših blokov z najvišjim na začetku ali od višine :start_height, če je podana.

trans-unit.source: Returns current mempool as projected blocks.
trans-unit.target: Vrne trenutni mempool, kot projekcijo blokov.

trans-unit.source: Returns our currently suggested fees for new transactions.
trans-unit.target: Vrne trenutno predlagano omrežnino za nove transakcije.

trans-unit.source: Returns all Bisq transactions belonging to a Bitcoin address, with 'B' prefixed in front of the address.
trans-unit.target: Vrne vse Bisq transakcije povezane z Bitcoin naslovom, pred naslovom se uporabi predpono 'B'.

trans-unit.source: Returns all Bisq transactions that exist in a Bitcoin block.
trans-unit.target: Vrne vse Bisq transakcije vsebovane v Bitcoin bloku.

trans-unit.source: Returns the most recently processed Bitcoin block height processed by Bisq.
trans-unit.target: Vrne višino najnovejšega Bitcoin bloka, ki vsebuje Bisq transakcije.

trans-unit.source: Returns :length Bitcoin blocks that contain Bisq transactions, starting from :index.
trans-unit.target: Vrne :length Bitcoin blokov, ki vsebujejo Bisq transakcije, z začetkom od :index.

trans-unit.source: Returns statistics about all Bisq transactions.
trans-unit.target: Vrne statistične podatke o vseh Bisq transakcijah.

trans-unit.source: Returns details about a Bisq transaction.
Returns :length of latest Bisq transactions, starting from :index.
trans-unit.target: Vrne :length zadnjih Bisq transakcij, z začetkom od :index.

trans-unit.source: Get the full list of txids in the mempool as an array. The order of the txids is arbitrary and does not match bitcoind.
trans-unit.target: Vrne celoten seznam txid-jev v mempoolu v obliki polja. Vrstni red txid-jev je arbitraren in se ne ujema z bitcoind.

trans-unit.source: Get a list of the last 10 transactions to enter the mempool. Each transaction object contains simplified overview data, with the following fields: txid, fee, vsize, and value.
trans-unit.target: Vrne seznam zadnjih 10 transakcij dodanih v mempool. Vsak objekt transakcije vsebuje naslednja polja: txid, fee, vsize, in value.

trans-unit.source: Returns the ancestors and the best descendant fees for a transaction.
trans-unit.target: Vrne prednike in najboljšo omrežnino za potomce transakcije.

trans-unit.source: Returns details about a transaction. Available fields: txid, version, locktime, size, weight, fee, vin, vout, and status.
trans-unit.target: Vrne podatke o transakciji. Razpoložljiva polja: txid, version, locktime, size, weight, fee, vin, vout, in status.

trans-unit.source: Returns a transaction serialized as hex.
Returns a merkle inclusion proof for the transaction using bitcoind's merkleblock format.
trans-unit.target: Vrne merkle dokaz o vsebovanosti za transakcijo (angl. merkle inclusion proof), v bitcoind's merkleblock obliki.

trans-unit.source: Returns a merkle inclusion proof for the transaction using Electrum's blockchain.transaction.get_merkle format.
trans-unit.target: Vrne merkle dokaz o vsebovanosti za transakcijo (angl. merkle inclusion proof), v Electrum blockchain.transaction.get_merkle obliki.

trans-unit.source: Returns the spending status of a transaction output. Available fields: spent (boolean), txid (optional), vin (optional), and status (optional, the status of the spending tx).
trans-unit.target: Vrne stanje porabe izhoda transakcije. Razpoložljiva polja: spent (boolean), txid (opcijsko), vin (opcijsko) in status (opcijsko, stanje potrditve transakcije).

trans-unit.source: Returns the spending status of all transaction outputs.
trans-unit.target: Vrne stanje porabe vseh izhodov transakcije.

trans-unit.source: Returns a transaction as binary data.
Returns the confirmation status of a transaction. Available fields: confirmed (boolean), block_height (optional), and block_hash (optional).
trans-unit.target: Vrne stanje potrditve transakcije. Razpoložljiva polja: confirmed (boolean), block_height (opcijsko) in block_hash (opcijsko).

trans-unit.source: Broadcast a raw transaction to the network. The transaction should be provided as hex in the request body. The txid will be returned on success.
trans-unit.target: V omrežju objavi neobdelano (raw) transakcijo. Transakcija mora biti podana v telesu zahteve v šestnajstiški obliki. Ob uspehu bo vrnjen txid.

trans-unit.source: Default push: action: 'want', data: ['blocks', ...] to express what you want pushed. Available: blocks, mempool-blocks, live-2h-chart, and stats.Push transactions related to address: 'track-address': '3PbJ...bF9B' to receive all new transactions containing that address as input or output. Returns an array of transactions. address-transactions for new mempool transactions, and block-transactions for new block confirmed transactions.
trans-unit.target: Začetni potisk: action: 'want', data: ['blocks', ...] za izbiro potisnih podatkov. Razpoložljivo: blocks, mempool-blocks, live-2h-chart in stats.Potisk transakcij povezanih z naslovom: 'track-address': '3PbJ...bF9B' za prejem vseh novih transakcij, ki vsebujejo ta naslov v vhodu ali izhodu. Vrne polje transakcij. address-transactions za nove transakcije v mempool-u in block-transactions za potrjene transakcije v novem bloku.
Napaka pri nalaganju podatkov o sredstvu.

trans-unit.source: Based on average native segwit transaction of 140 vBytes
trans-unit.target: Na podlagi povprečne native segwit transakcije (140 vBajtov).

trans-unit.note: Total subsidy and fees in a block

trans-unit.source: TXID, block height, hash or address
trans-unit.target: TXID, višina bloka, hash ali naslov

trans-unit.source: This transaction has been replaced by:
trans-unit.target: Ta transakcija je bila nadomeščena z:

trans-unit.note: Transaction ETA in several hours or more

trans-unit.source: Waiting for it to appear in the mempool...
trans-unit.target: Čakanje, da se prikaže v mempool-u...

trans-unit.source: This transaction saved % on fees by using native SegWit-Bech32
trans-unit.target: Ta transakcija je prihranila % omrežnine z uporabo native SegWit-Bech32.

trans-unit.source: This transaction saved % on fees by using SegWit and could save % more by fully upgrading to native SegWit-Bech32
trans-unit.target: Ta transakcija je prihranila % omrežnine z uporabo SegWit in bi lahko dodatnih % s popolno nadgradnjo na native SegWit-Bech32.

trans-unit.source: This transaction could save % on fees by upgrading to native SegWit-Bech32 or % by upgrading to SegWit-P2SH
trans-unit.target: Ta transakcija bi lahko prihranila % omrežnine z nadgradnjo na native SegWit-Bech32 ali % z nadgradnjo na SegWit-P2SH.

trans-unit.source: This transaction support Replace-By-Fee (RBF) allowing fee bumping
trans-unit.target: Ta transakcija omogoča povečanje omrežnine, Replace-By-Fee (RBF).

trans-unit.source: This transaction does NOT support Replace-By-Fee (RBF) and cannot be fee bumped using this method
trans-unit.target: Ta transakcija NE omogoča povečanja omrežnine, z uporabo Replace-By-Fee (RBF).

trans-unit.source: Only ~ sat/vB was needed to get into this block
trans-unit.target: Samo ~ sat/vB je bilo potrebno za vključitev v ta blok.
